quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,Nuun- (edde faxem Yalli yaaxige) Yalli Qhalam kee yaktube mari uktubbu haamal xiibite
  68,2,Atu Nabiyow ku Rabbi koh yecee niqmatih sabbatah cabuli akke waytaamal xiibite
  68,3,Kaadu diggah atu galtoy aggiriqqe sinni litoomul xiibite
  68,4,Kaadu diggah atu naba caalat maqaaneh bagul tantoomul xiibite
  68,5,"Xayi waktit Nabiyow atu ablettooh, usun (koros kinnuk) ablelon"
  68,6,Siinik cabulem kinni num abletton koo kinnik ken kinnim
  68,7,"Diggah ku Rabbi usuk ixxigah yayse Rabbi kinni kay gitak makkooteh yan marat, kaadu usuk ixxigah yayse Rabbi kinni kay gital tirri iyyeeh kaal diggi iyye marat"
  68,8,Toysa isi diinil diggi xicaay moggolin koo kee Qhuraan dirabboyse mara
  68,9,"Kaadu Nabiyow atu usun faxe waanamak tu cabtaamal keenih xabbacowtek, usun kaadu koh xabbacoowaanam faxan"
  68,10,Kaadu ummaan numwy xiiba maggoy bayoytah yanih yab moggolin
  68,11,Cami maggo numwy sittal hayah sinam fanal gexaah yangagayyeh yab moggolin
  68,12,"Cinnaaneynay kayri celli haytam gibdi waasoh waasay caddok taturlih yaniy, dambi maggoh yab moggolin"
  68,13,"Koroosanni maggah Sorkocobbaxi kak kafe numvuy, tohuk lakal ilmoytah yani kinni"
  68,14,"Usuk a weelot kah weeloysimem, maali gaddaa kee xalay mangintah sabbata"
  68,15,"Ni-aayoota (Qhuraan kinnuk) kaal tankirriyime waqdi, ah naharsi marih hayyayyoona iyya anqasah"
  68,16,Xayi uddurul (waktil) kate waa bedu kaak heenno sanal
  68,17,"Diggah nanu makki mara qulul kee qabaarat niqiyyire bustaan mara kah niqiyyire innah, usun subci wakti kay caxammixu tumaleelak qellut yargiqoonu waanamah xiibiten waqdi"
  68,18,Yalli faxek maxaccinnon
  68,19,Tokkel ku Rabbih kabuk usun xiinit anuk mire (giráy kaa carrisse kinnuk) kaa mireh
  68,20,Tokkel usuk data gommod ceelak maacise
  68,21,Tokke sittah kayam kaayeenih maacisen waqdi
  68,22,Sinni buqree kee sinni caxammixuh waqlal kuula kaa yargaqu waah orbisa mara tekkeenik ittak iyyen
  68,23,"Tokkel gexeenih, usun tutuc axcuk"
  68,24,Ta saaku tumaleela bustaan siinil cule waytaama ittak axcuk
  68,25,Kuuleenih loowiteenimil dudda le mara sinni akka luk
  68,26,"Tokkel usun sinni bustaan carareeh gombod yekkem yublen waqdi, diggaluk nanu baditneeh gitak hoxneh nan iyyen"
  68,27,"Usun Bustaan sinni bustaan kinnim yismiten waqdi: Wonna hinnay nanu kay kayrik baxaysite mara nekke, tumaleela cakkik kak waasneemih sabbatah iyyen"
  68,28,"Keenik kas kee kayrih yayse num: siinik maxaccinniyoo, Yalla ma saytunnossaanaa, Yalli saytunih itteenih, hinnay Yalli faxek itteenih"
  68,29,"Nanu ni Rabbi kaah yaguude saytunnoysiyyah kaa saytunnosna, diggah nanu ninni nafsi yudlume marah sugne tumaleela cakkik waasneemil"
  68,30,Tokkel gari garut keenik yufkune sitta assacakkuk
  68,31,"Booley nee gee finqgaaw! Diggah nanu caddok tatre marah sugne, Yallih amri cinneeh tumaleela cakkik waasne waqdi"
  68,32,"Ni Rabbi nanu abneh nan umaanek kaal gacneemih sabbatah, tama bustaanak taysem nee ciggiilisele, diggaak nanu ninni Rabbik qafuu kee muxxo qaagitna"
  68,33,"Addunyâ digaalá Tonna. Diggah akeerâ digaalá wohuuk naba, usun woh yaaxige mara akkinnoonuy waasimak yenen"